rows.label: tlk4571014101_msg0001
rows.name:
I heard all about Damida.
And how I was under suspicion.

rows.label: tlk4571014101_msg0002
rows.name:
Don't worry, I'm not blaming you.
You did the rational thing.

rows.label: tlk4571014101_msg0003
rows.name:
Communicating isn't my strong point.
I'm used to people getting the wrong
end of the stick.

rows.label: tlk4571014101_msg0004
rows.name:
All I can do is prove my reliability
by doing good work out in the field.
A mercenary is judged by his skills.
